<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-bg"></div>
  <header class="site-header">
    <a class="brand" href="/">
      <span class="brand-mark">AI</span>
      <span class="brand-text">Recipe Planner</span>
    </a>
    <nav class="top-nav">
      <a href="/">Landing</a>
      <a href="/chat-ai">Chat AI</a>
      <a href="/chat-history">Chat History</a>
      <a href="/api/recipes">Recipes API</a>
    </nav>
    <a class="nav-cta" href="/">Home</a>
  </header>

  <main class="chat-layout">
    <section class="chat-panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <span class="section-kicker">Chat AI</span>
        <h1>Uji percakapan AI untuk resep dan meal planning.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Tulis bahan, budget, atau tujuan makan kamu. Respons dihasilkan dari Gemini free tier dan histori chat disimpan per sesi.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="chat-window" id="chatWindow" aria-live="polite"></div>

      <form class="chat-form" id="chatForm">
        <textarea id="chatInput" rows="3" placeholder="Contoh: saya punya telur, mie, dan ayam. Buatkan menu hemat untuk 3 hari."></textarea>
        <div class="chat-actions">
          <button type="submit" class="button button-primary">Kirim</button>
          <button type="button" class="button button-secondary" id="resetChat">Reset chat</button>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/chat-history">Lihat history</a>
        </div>
      </form>
    </section>

    <aside class="side-panel">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-badge">01</div>
        <h3>Prompt cepat</h3>
        <p>Kirim konteks singkat untuk cek arah jawaban AI.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-badge">02</div>
        <h3>Output terstruktur</h3>
        <p>Response dibikin dalam format yang gampang dirender di UI.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-badge">03</div>
        <h3>Histori tersimpan</h3>
        <p>Setiap pesan user dan jawaban AI masuk ke database per sesi.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </main>

  <script>
    window.__INITIAL_CHAT_MESSAGES__ = <%- JSON.stringify(messages || []) %>;
  </script>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
